ocean_s.formula:
z(n,k,j,i) = eta(n,j,i)*(1+s(k)) and depth_c*s(k) and (depth(j,i)-depth_c)*C(k) 
 where 
 C(k)=(1-b)*sinh(a*s(k))/sinh(a) +
   b*(tanh(a*(s(k)+0.5))/(2*tanh(0.5*a)) - 0.5)
